{"search_data": "OdishaMadhu Babu Pension Yojana \u2013 Old Age Pension Scheme in OdishaPayout under Madhu Babu Pension YojanaThe beneficiaries of age group of 60 to 79 years would get Rs 300 per month and those above of 80 years and above would get Rs. 500 per month as pension.The pension amount normally gets transferred on 15th of every month to the bank account of the beneficiary. However, beneficiary can also choose to disburse the pension amount on the Jan Seva Diwas at the Gram Panchayat Office or Block Development Office.Eligibility for Madhu Babu Pension Yojana"}